    {
      "id": "66dbb422-5630-4ac7-a0f0-2ffaa8dada5e",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer qu'il existe un uni\\-que polyn{\\^o}me\n     $P_n \\in { K[X]}$ tel que $P_n(X) + P_n(X+1) = 2X^n$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer qu’il existe un unique polyn<span>ô</span>me <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P_n \\in { K[X]}\\)</span> tel que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P_n(X) + P_n(X+1) = 2X^n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "76b8aa37-2973-4de7-aca0-352ffb4aabb5",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Isomorphisme $P \\longmapsto P(X) + P(X+1)$.",
        "html": "<p>Isomorphisme <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P \\longmapsto P(X) + P(X+1)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "3eafb4d6-0892-48aa-9c67-9697bf8a52df",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Chercher une relation de r{\\'e}currence entre $P_n'$ et $P_{n-1}$.",
        "html": "<p>Chercher une relation de r<span>é</span>currence entre <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P_n&#39;\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P_{n-1}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e6332594-0dea-4483-bdf3-9f0aeb1b43f7",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$P_n' = nP_{n-1}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(P_n&#39; = nP_{n-1}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "9250d307-9164-4df6-8d07-90a2521e0395",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "D{\\'e}composer $P_n(X+1)$ sur la base $(P_k)_{k \\in \\N}$.",
        "html": "<p>D<span>é</span>composer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P_n(X+1)\\)</span> sur la base <span class=\"math inline\">\\((P_k)_{k \\in \\N}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "b370d690-c6aa-4e3b-90a7-133379d3b2e4",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$P_n(X+1) = \\sum_{k=0}^n C_n^k P_k$\\quad (Taylor).",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(P_n(X+1) = \\sum_{k=0}^n C_n^k P_k\\)</span>(Taylor).</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "79e1c3da-c46d-48a5-85b6-6efdc90c7118",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "D{\\'e}montrer que $P_n(1-X) = (-1)^nP_n(X)$.",
        "html": "<p>D<span>é</span>montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P_n(1-X) = (-1)^nP_n(X)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "010cba89-0457-43cb-a03f-2df68b64f7a5",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$Q_n(X) = P_n(1-X)  \\Rightarrow  Q_n(X) + Q_n(X+1) = 2(-1)^nX^n$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(Q_n(X) = P_n(1-X)  \\Rightarrow  Q_n(X) + Q_n(X+1) = 2(-1)^nX^n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
